ugin-import/commit/ccd93942a0b9f59f1b698672ba167ece1aa9f5f1\"><code>ccd9394</code></a> docs(readme): add space (#&#8203;888)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/benmosher/eslint-plugin-import/commit/2f2dfb0a818f0c5cc6f5939627568636548bce97\"><code>2f2dfb0</code></a> cleanup: no exclusive tests</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/benmosher/eslint-plugin-import/commit/ed65a7412a90f4e3cf475efaff7a8ea001d6adc1\"><code>ed65a74</code></a> logic: improve scoped module scoping</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/benmosher/eslint-plugin-import/commit/307ddeb587ce5abc382e9c827da045f0e5dcb292\"><code>307ddeb</code></a> cleanup: no exclusive tests</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/benmosher/eslint-plugin-import/commit/dbc9ec735d9fd32ae69499c235f2a0deb106be94\"><code>dbc9ec7</code></a> bugfix: #&#8203;886</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
